data.description: Beautiful brick home on land in the quiet, quaint community of Tehuacana, TX! This spacious brick home has so much to offer for your growing needs! This property is approximately 1.6-2 +- acres of open and treed land. The back yard includes fencing and beautiful shade trees for the kiddos and animals to play and roam. The interior features a spacious family room with vaulted ceilings, wbfp, built in cabinetry and french pocket doors that lead to the encl Sunroom-solarium. The wall of windows offer nice views of the shaded back yard and lots of natural light. The large Dining Room is perfect for hosting large fgatherings and entertaining. Upstairs a 21x25 bonus rm is perfect as a gameroom for the kiddos, a mancave for dad or perfect as a guest suite. Other features incl an Eat-in Kitchen, office space w-a wall of custom cabinetry and lots of storage closets. The garage is large enough for 2 vehicles and additional storage.
